# CLIP ChangeLog for app-arch/bzip2

*openldap-2.4.38-r7 (18 Sep 2017)

  18 Sep 2017; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openldap-2.4.38-r7.ebuild, -openldap-2.4.38-r6.ebuild:
  Rbump to link with icu 58.2.

*openldap-2.4.38-r6 (23 Mar 2016)

  23 Mar 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
