*openldap-2.4.23 (06 Aug 2010)

  06 Aug 2010; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openldap-2.4.23.ebuild, -openldap-2.3.43.ebuild:
  Bump to latest main stream stable (2.4.23), using latest portage
  ebuild (2.4.21). Same CLIP change set.
  Fixes CVE-2010-0211 and CVE-2010-0212.

*openldap-2.3.43 (14 Apr 2009)

  14 Apr 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openldap-2.3.43.ebuild, -openldap-2.3.30-r2.ebuild:
  Bump to latest stable, same CLIP change set.
  Fixes compile issues with glibc-2.8, and GLSA-200808-09 DoS
  vulnerability (CVE-2008-2952).

25 Nov 2008; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openldap-2.3.30-r2.ebuild:
  Change the ldap.conf if the clip use flag is set.

*openldap-2.3.30-r2.ebuild

24 Nov 2008; Olivier Levillain <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openldap-2.3.30-r2.ebuild:
  Initial CLIP import. Add IUSE clip to install the library (and
  only it) for the ldap clients.

